title: Exception thrown when exporting data from a table inside a grid cell
EB: When exporting data from two tables, the expected result is that the data should be successfully exported. However, the actual result is that an exception is thrown in the 'ReportEngineService.getMetaData()' function.
SR: To reproduce the issue: 1. Insert one table into one grid cell. 2. Insert another table into the other grid cell.
